1
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:37,160
I'm sorry, I drank too much yesterday

2
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:40,710
Drink

3
00:00:41,790 --> 00:00:43,290
No, I have a class

4
00:00:44,540 --> 00:00:45,340
I also have a class

5
00:00:45,880 --> 00:00:46,710
Drink

6
00:00:48,630 --> 00:00:50,170
It's really okay

7
00:00:55,260 --> 00:00:55,850
Over there

8
00:00:56,220 --> 00:00:57,470
Aren't you angry?

9
00:00:58,100 --> 00:00:58,480
Angry?

10
00:00:59,730 --> 00:01:00,600
Is it me?

11
00:01:01,310 --> 00:01:03,060
No, that's not it

12
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:07,440
- So it’s not even worth getting angry...

13
00:01:20,910 --> 00:01:22,960
Of course it's cold when you dress like this in the cold wave

14
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:25,920
It's okay, I'm not cold at all...

15
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,230
Hurry up and put it on me

16
00:01:47,940 --> 00:01:48,650
Ah

17
00:02:15,300 --> 00:02:16,510
Listen to the class diligently

18
00:02:23,350 --> 00:02:24,690
- How was it after trying to give a lecture?

19
00:02:25,940 --> 00:02:27,100
It's fun

20
00:02:27,730 --> 00:02:30,110
Other professors also take good care of us

21
00:02:30,730 --> 00:02:31,780
- Who is the department head again?

22
00:02:32,650 --> 00:02:33,240
Professor Heo

23
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:34,700
Ah...

24
00:02:35,490 --> 00:02:37,870
- Professor Heo, don't you drink with the students these days?

25
00:02:38,370 --> 00:02:40,530
Well, I'm not sure

26
00:02:41,410 --> 00:02:41,790
Why?

27
00:02:42,830 --> 00:02:45,580
- Professor Heo had a scandal with a female student a few years ago

28
00:02:46,620 --> 00:02:48,210
- They say we just got along well

29
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:50,630
- The female student dropped out because of rumors about compensated dating,

30
00:02:51,130 --> 00:02:52,630
- Professor Heo is also struggling

31
00:02:53,550 --> 00:02:55,430
- It seems like taking a sabbatical is okay after all

32
00:02:56,550 --> 00:02:58,550
- Only the female students are pitiful

33
00:03:10,230 --> 00:03:10,900
Why?

34
00:03:11,690 --> 00:03:14,440
I'm going to return the scarf

35
00:03:19,530 --> 00:03:20,820
Just take it

36
00:03:23,330 --> 00:03:24,620
Please buy me dinner

37
00:03:25,410 --> 00:03:26,000
Busy

38
00:03:26,540 --> 00:03:27,790
Then please buy me a coffee

39
00:03:28,670 --> 00:03:29,750
I don't drink coffee

40
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:32,170
You can just drink something else

41
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:33,710
Busy

42
00:03:35,170 --> 00:03:36,220
If you have nothing to say, leave

43
00:03:38,050 --> 00:03:39,430
Why are you doing this to me?

44
00:03:40,930 --> 00:03:42,560
Why were you so nice to me?

45
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:46,270
You should have just gotten angry and kicked me out

46
00:03:46,270 --> 00:03:47,690
instead of coming to find me after drinking

47
00:03:48,230 --> 00:03:50,150
Why are you confusing people?

48
00:03:52,060 --> 00:03:53,400
Do you have feelings for me?

49
00:03:54,570 --> 00:03:56,280
Or are you just too tired to be angry now?

50
00:04:03,950 --> 00:04:05,120
Don't be mistaken

51
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,870
You don't do anything for me

52
00:04:20,930 --> 00:04:24,260
- Excuse me, are you Lee Ho-won from the Business Administration department?

53
00:04:24,930 --> 00:04:26,220
Yes, but?

54
00:04:26,470 --> 00:04:28,690
Don't you remember that I took the liberal arts class with you?

55
00:04:28,850 --> 00:04:29,890
- Don't you remember?

56
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:31,900
That English literature class

57
00:04:36,230 --> 00:04:37,820
You don't remember, huh?

58
00:04:38,570 --> 00:04:40,570
If you don't have a girlfriend, perhaps...

59
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:42,700
Could you give me your number?

60
00:04:51,540 --> 00:04:52,290
Of course

61
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,580
I think I remember now

62
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,670
- Oh, really?

63
00:04:57,380 --> 00:04:58,800
You look so beautiful that I didn't recognize you

64
00:04:59,260 --> 00:05:00,720
Let's keep in touch

65
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:08,100
Hey!

66
00:05:08,890 --> 00:05:11,100
I posted the photo we took together on Instagram

67
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,850
A senior I know asked me to introduce you

68
00:05:14,610 --> 00:05:16,650
It's okay, I don't need an introduction

69
00:05:17,610 --> 00:05:18,900
So, would you like to add me as an Instagram friend?

70
00:05:20,740 --> 00:05:21,450
- Hello

71
00:05:22,070 --> 00:05:22,780
Yes

72
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:29,790
You're totally begging for your own style

73
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:31,460
Really?

74
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:34,380
Then let me know if I can add you as a friend on Instagram

75
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,130
- Envious little one

76
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:38,630
- Popular little one

77
00:05:49,850 --> 00:05:51,020
Professor!

78
00:05:57,110 --> 00:05:58,150
Are you leaving work?

79
00:06:00,230 --> 00:06:00,780
Yes

80
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:02,320
So?

81
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:04,280
Please give me a ride

82
00:06:07,700 --> 00:06:09,160
How far do you want to take me?

83
00:06:09,870 --> 00:06:11,080
To the front of the station

84
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:15,120
Oh, or is the professor passing by Itaewon?

85
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,960
Yeah, he is passing by

86
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:20,500
Then please drop me off at Itaewon Station

87
00:06:31,060 --> 00:06:32,140
Hello?

88
00:06:32,890 --> 00:06:33,600
Hyung!

89
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:35,600
I'm leaving now

90
00:06:37,020 --> 00:06:38,480
I don't think it will be late?

91
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:41,940
Oh, really?

92
00:06:43,780 --> 00:06:46,070
I'm really hungry right now

93
00:06:47,740 --> 00:06:49,780
Okay, I'm looking forward to it?

94
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,080
Yeah

95
00:06:58,460 --> 00:06:59,500
Why?

96
00:07:01,670 --> 00:07:02,590
Just

97
00:07:03,710 --> 00:07:04,760
I thought it changed a bit

98
00:07:07,300 --> 00:07:09,350
I was a bit hurt, but

99
00:07:09,890 --> 00:07:10,970
I've sorted out my feelings

100
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:14,180
- I told the professor that I'm nothing special

101
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,390
Don't be awkward, let's get along well

102
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,310
There are many people who like me, so what?

103
00:07:21,570 --> 00:07:22,820
Be careful about who you meet

104
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:25,280
Don't get hurt for no reason

105
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:27,860
What is it?

106
00:07:28,820 --> 00:07:29,910
Why are you worried about me?

107
00:07:31,450 --> 00:07:33,080
Are you a bit disappointed now?

108
00:07:34,290 --> 00:07:35,330
Am I jealous?

109
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:41,000
- I'm just joking

110
00:07:59,140 --> 00:08:00,730
- I told you to put it down!

111
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:10,950
I told you to put this down

112
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:13,450
What are you doing coming all the way to school?

113
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,790
You never answer my calls

114
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:19,330
I didn't contact you because I didn't want to see you, hyung

115
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:22,000
Damn it, why does everything have to go your way?

116
00:08:23,130 --> 00:08:24,630
- When you're bored, you play with it

117
00:08:24,630 --> 00:08:26,550
and then throw it away because it loses its charm, right?

118
00:08:27,670 --> 00:08:28,550
That's not it

119
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,090
Do I have to leave if you say so?

120
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:33,760
If the other person doesn't like it, it's right to let them go

121
00:08:35,180 --> 00:08:36,180
Son of a bitch

122
00:08:36,810 --> 00:08:38,270
Where are you going to wag your tail this time?

123
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:40,560
Let's not talk about it

124
00:08:40,890 --> 00:08:42,020
Talk to me before you go

125
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:43,020
Let go -

126
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:44,770
I'm talking!

127
00:08:44,770 --> 00:08:45,480
Where do you think

128
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,860
you're going?

129
00:08:47,610 --> 00:08:48,190
- I have a class!

130
00:08:48,690 --> 00:08:49,450
Come here

131
00:08:49,740 --> 00:08:50,450
Put it down!

132
00:08:50,450 --> 00:08:51,450
Let's talk
